ORGAN SERIES - NFT - BRAIN

Human Brain is the most advanced Biological Neural Engine present on this planet Earth.

1.Limited to a total of three variants.

2.Variant-1: DWOS-01 "RED BRAIN"
    Variant-2: DWOS-02 "SILVER BRAIN"
    Variant-3: DWOS-03 "GOLD BRAIN"


Human Body is packed with an astonishing 78 organs each with a special feature.
From Incredible discoveries to important inventions this human body never stops and the saga still continue.
From Earth to Moon to Metaverse to Mars seems like nothing is impossible for this Human Body.

It's our honour to showcase these organs of human body for the upcoming universe of Metaverse.

RED: Represents Biological Strength of Human Body
SILVER: Represents Undying Power of Human Body
GOLD: Represents Unbelievable Achievements of Human Body
